<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>i9Treino — Seu treino, do seu jeito, em qualquer lugar</title>
<meta name="theme-color" content="#0d0d0d">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Sora:wght@400;600;700;800&family=Outfit:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root{
    --bg:#0d0d0d;
    --surface:#161616;
    --surface2:#1e1e1e;
    --surface3:#262626;
    --border:#2e2e2e;
    --accent:#c8f542;
    --accent2:#a8d932;
    --text:#f5f5f0;
    --text-dim:#9a9a93;
    --text-dimmer:#6b6b66;
  }
  *{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box;}
  html{scroll-behavior:smooth;}
  body{
    background:var(--bg);
    color:var(--text);
    font-family:'Outfit',sans-serif;
    line-height:1.6;
    overflow-x:hidden;
  }
  h1,h2,h3,h4,.display{
    font-family:'Sora',sans-serif;
    font-weight:800;
    letter-spacing:-0.02em;
    line-height:1.08;
  }
  a{color:inherit;text-decoration:none;}
  img{max-width:100%;display:block;}
  .wrap{max-width:1140px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 24px;}
  .accent{color:var(--accent);}

  /* ---------- Nav ---------- */
  header{
    position:sticky;top:0;z-index:100;
    background:rgba(13,13,13,0.85);
    backdrop-filter:blur(12px);
    border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);
  }
  nav{
    display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;
    padding:16px 24px;max-width:1140px;margin:0 auto;
  }
  .logo{
    font-family:'Sora',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:1.4rem;
    letter-spacing:-0.03em;
  }
  .logo span{color:var(--accent);}
  .nav-cta{
    background:var(--accent);color:var(--bg);
    padding:10px 22px;border-radius:999px;
    font-weight:700;font-size:0.92rem;
    transition:transform .15s ease, box-shadow .15s ease;
    white-space:nowrap;
  }
  .nav-cta:hover{transform:translateY(-2px);box-shadow:0 8px 24px -8px var(--accent);}

  /* ---------- Hero ---------- */
  .hero{
    position:relative;
    padding:90px 0 80px;
    overflow:hidden;
  }
  .hero::before{
    content:'';
    position:absolute;
    top:-200px;right:-200px;
    width:600px;height:600px;
    background:radial-gradient(circle, rgba(200,245,66,0.18), transparent 70%);
    pointer-events:none;
  }
  .hero-grid{
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns:1.1fr 0.9fr;
    gap:48px;
    align-items:center;
    position:relative;
    z-index:1;
  }
  .eyebrow{
    display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;
    border:1px solid var(--border);
    background:var(--surface);
    padding:7px 16px;border-radius:999px;
    font-size:0.82rem;color:var(--text-dim);
    margin-bottom:24px;
    font-weight:500;
  }
  .eyebrow::before{
    content:'';width:7px;height:7px;border-radius:50%;
    background:var(--accent);
    box-shadow:0 0 0 0 rgba(200,245,66,0.5);
    animation:pulse 2s infinite;
  }
  @keyframes pulse{
    0%{box-shadow:0 0 0 0 rgba(200,245,66,0.5);}
    70%{box-shadow:0 0 0 8px rgba(200,245,66,0);}
    100%{box-shadow:0 0 0 0 rgba(200,245,66,0);}
  }
  .hero h1{
    font-size:clamp(2.4rem, 5.5vw, 3.8rem);
    margin-bottom:20px;
  }
  .hero p.lead{
    font-size:1.1rem;color:var(--text-dim);
    max-width:480px;margin-bottom:32px;
  }
  .hero-actions{display:flex;gap:14px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:28px;}
  .btn{
    display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:10px;
    padding:16px 28px;border-radius:999px;
    font-weight:700;font-size:1rem;
    border:none;cursor:pointer;
    transition:transform .15s ease, box-shadow .15s ease, background .15s ease;
    font-family:'Outfit',sans-serif;
  }
  .btn-primary{
    background:var(--accent);color:var(--bg);
  }
  .btn-primary:hover{transform:translateY(-2px);box-shadow:0 10px 30px -10px var(--accent);}
  .btn-ghost{
    background:transparent;color:var(--text);
    border:1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .btn-ghost:hover{border-color:var(--accent);color:var(--accent);}
  .hero-proof{
    display:flex;gap:28px;flex-wrap:wrap;
    color:var(--text-dim);font-size:0.88rem;
  }
  .hero-proof div{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;}
  .hero-proof svg{flex-shrink:0;color:var(--accent);}

  /* Hero visual */
  .hero-visual{
    position:relative;
    display:flex;justify-content:center;
  }
  .phone{
    width:280px;
    background:var(--surface);
    border:1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius:32px;
    padding:18px;
    box-shadow:0 30px 80px -30px rgba(0,0,0,0.8);
    position:relative;
  }
  .phone-screen{
    background:var(--bg);
    border-radius:20px;
    padding:20px 16px;
    min-height:420px;
  }
  .phone-app-name{font-size:1.05rem;font-weight:800;margin-bottom:4px;}
  .phone-app-sub{font-size:0.78rem;color:var(--text-dim);margin-bottom:20px;}
  .phone-card{
    background:var(--surface2);
    border:1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius:14px;
    padding:14px;margin-bottom:12px;
  }
  .phone-card-title{font-size:0.85rem;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:6px;}
  .phone-card-meta{font-size:0.74rem;color:var(--text-dim);}
  .phone-row{
    display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;
    margin-top:10px;padding-top:10px;border-top:1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .phone-tag{
    display:inline-block;
    background:rgba(200,245,66,0.12);color:var(--accent);
    font-size:0.7rem;font-weight:700;
    padding:3px 10px;border-radius:999px;
  }
  .load-input{
    background:var(--surface3);border:1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius:8px;padding:6px 10px;
    font-size:0.78rem;color:var(--text);
    width:56px;text-align:center;
    font-family:'Outfit',sans-serif;
  }
  .float-badge{
    position:absolute;
    background:var(--surface2);
    border:1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius:14px;
    padding:12px 16px;
    display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;
    box-shadow:0 20px 50px -20px rgba(0,0,0,0.7);
    font-size:0.82rem;font-weight:600;
  }
  .float-badge.b1{top:60px;left:-30px;}
  .float-badge.b2{bottom:90px;right:-36px;}
  .float-badge svg{color:var(--accent);}

  /* ---------- Sections shared ---------- */
  section{padding:90px 0;}
  .section-head{
    text-align:center;max-width:680px;margin:0 auto 56px;
  }
  .section-head .eyebrow{margin-bottom:18px;}
  .section-head h2{font-size:clamp(1.9rem, 4vw, 2.7rem);margin-bottom:14px;}
  .section-head p{color:var(--text-dim);font-size:1.05rem;}

  /* ---------- Problem section ---------- */
  .problem{background:var(--surface);border-top:1px solid var(--border);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);}
  .problem-grid{
    display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:24px;
  }
  .problem-card{
    background:var(--surface2);
    border:1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius:18px;
    padding:28px;
  }
  .problem-card .icon{
    width:46px;height:46px;border-radius:12px;
    background:var(--surface3);
    display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
    margin-bottom:18px;color:var(--accent);
  }
  .problem-card h3{font-size:1.1rem;margin-bottom:10px;font-weight:700;}
  .problem-card p{color:var(--text-dim);font-size:0.94rem;}

  /* ---------- Modalidades ---------- */
  .modalities-grid{
    display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:18px;
  }
  .mod-card{
    background:var(--surface);
    border:1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius:18px;
    padding:26px 22px;
    transition:border-color .2s ease, transform .2s ease;
  }
  .mod-card:hover{border-color:var(--accent);transform:translateY(-4px);}
  .mod-num{
    font-family:'Sora',sans-serif;font-weight:800;
    font-size:0.78rem;color:var(--text-dimmer);
    letter-spacing:0.08em;margin-bottom:14px;
  }
  .mod-card h3{font-size:1.15rem;margin-bottom:8px;}
  .mod-card p{color:var(--text-dim);font-size:0.88rem;}

  /* ---------- Protocolos por gênero/frequência ---------- */
  .protocols{background:var(--surface);border-top:1px solid var(--border);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);}
  .protocols-tabs{
    display:flex;justify-content:center;gap:10px;margin-bottom:40px;flex-wrap:wrap;
  }
  .ptab{
    background:var(--surface2);border:1px solid var(--border);
    color:var(--text-dim);font-weight:700;font-size:0.9rem;
    padding:11px 24px;border-radius:999px;cursor:pointer;
    transition:all .15s ease;font-family:'Outfit',sans-serif;
  }
  .ptab.active{background:var(--accent);color:var(--bg);border-color:var(--accent);}
  .ptab:hover:not(.active){border-color:var(--accent);color:var(--accent);}

  .freq-grid{
    display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(5,1fr);gap:14px;margin-bottom:56px;
  }
  .freq-card{
    background:var(--surface2);border:1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius:16px;padding:22px 14px;text-align:center;
    transition:border-color .2s ease, transform .2s ease;
  }
  .freq-card:hover{border-color:var(--accent);transform:translateY(-3px);}
  .freq-num{
    font-family:'Sora',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:2rem;
    color:var(--accent);line-height:1;margin-bottom:4px;
  }
  .freq-label{font-size:0.78rem;color:var(--text-dim);font-weight:600;}
  .freq-level{font-size:0.74rem;color:var(--text-dimmer);margin-top:6px;}

  .objectives-grid{
    display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:16px;margin-bottom:56px;
  }
  .objective-card{
    background:var(--surface2);border:1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius:16px;padding:24px 20px;
  }
  .objective-card .icon{
    width:42px;height:42px;border-radius:11px;
    background:var(--surface3);
    display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
    margin-bottom:14px;color:var(--accent);
  }
  .objective-card h4{font-size:1.02rem;margin-bottom:8px;font-weight:700;}
  .objective-card p{color:var(--text-dim);font-size:0.86rem;}

  .muscle-block h3.sub-h{
    font-size:1.3rem;text-align:center;margin-bottom:8px;
  }
  .muscle-block .sub-p{
    text-align:center;color:var(--text-dim);font-size:0.95rem;
    max-width:560px;margin:0 auto 32px;
  }
  .muscle-grid{
    display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit, minmax(130px, 1fr));
    gap:10px;
  }
  .muscle-chip{
    background:var(--surface2);border:1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius:12px;padding:16px 14px;
    text-align:center;font-size:0.88rem;font-weight:600;
    color:var(--text-dim);
    transition:all .15s ease;
  }
  .muscle-chip:hover{border-color:var(--accent);color:var(--accent);transform:translateY(-2px);}

  /* ---------- Como funciona ---------- */
  .how{background:var(--surface);border-top:1px solid var(--border);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);}
  .how-grid{
    display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);
    gap:0;position:relative;
  }
  .how-step{
    padding:0 20px;position:relative;
  }
  .how-step:not(:last-child)::after{
    content:'';position:absolute;top:24px;right:-2px;
    width:calc(100% - 48px);height:1px;
    background:repeating-linear-gradient(to right, var(--border) 0 6px, transparent 6px 12px);
    display:none;
  }
  @media(min-width:860px){
    .how-step:not(:last-child)::after{display:block;}
  }
  .how-step .step-num{
    font-family:'Sora',sans-serif;font-weight:800;
    font-size:2.4rem;color:var(--accent);
    margin-bottom:14px;line-height:1;
  }
  .how-step h3{font-size:1.05rem;margin-bottom:8px;}
  .how-step p{color:var(--text-dim);font-size:0.88rem;}

  /* ---------- Pricing ---------- */
  .pricing-grid{
    display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:22px;
    align-items:stretch;
  }
  .price-card{
    background:var(--surface);
    border:1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius:20px;
    padding:32px 28px;
    display:flex;flex-direction:column;
    position:relative;
  }
  .price-card.featured{
    border-color:var(--accent);
    background:linear-gradient(160deg, var(--surface2), var(--surface));
  }
  .price-badge{
    position:absolute;top:-13px;right:28px;
    background:var(--accent);color:var(--bg);
    font-size:0.74rem;font-weight:800;
    padding:5px 14px;border-radius:999px;
    letter-spacing:0.04em;
  }
  .price-card h3{font-size:1.2rem;margin-bottom:6px;}
  .price-card .price-tagline{color:var(--text-dim);font-size:0.86rem;margin-bottom:22px;}
  .price-value{
    display:flex;align-items:baseline;gap:6px;margin-bottom:6px;
  }
  .price-value .currency{font-size:1.1rem;color:var(--text-dim);font-weight:600;}
  .price-value .amount{
    font-family:'Sora',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:2.6rem;
  }
  .price-value .period{color:var(--text-dim);font-size:0.92rem;}
  .price-note{font-size:0.8rem;color:var(--text-dimmer);margin-bottom:24px;}
  .price-features{list-style:none;margin-bottom:28px;flex-grow:1;}
  .price-features li{
    display:flex;gap:10px;align-items:flex-start;
    font-size:0.9rem;color:var(--text-dim);
    margin-bottom:12px;
  }
  .price-features li svg{flex-shrink:0;margin-top:2px;color:var(--accent);}
  .price-features li.muted{color:var(--text-dimmer);}
  .price-features li.muted svg{color:var(--text-dimmer);}
  .price-cta{
    display:block;text-align:center;
    padding:14px 0;border-radius:999px;
    font-weight:700;font-size:0.96rem;
    border:1px solid var(--border);
    transition:all .15s ease;
  }
  .price-card.featured .price-cta{
    background:var(--accent);color:var(--bg);border-color:var(--accent);
  }
  .price-cta:hover{border-color:var(--accent);color:var(--accent);}
  .price-card.featured .price-cta:hover{
    background:var(--accent2);color:var(--bg);
  }
  .pricing-disclaimer{
    text-align:center;color:var(--text-dimmer);font-size:0.85rem;
    margin-top:32px;
  }

  /* ---------- Depoimentos / social proof placeholder ---------- */
  .social{background:var(--surface);border-top:1px solid var(--border);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);}
  .social-grid{
    display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:22px;
  }
  .social-card{
    background:var(--surface2);border:1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius:18px;padding:26px;
  }
  .social-stars{color:var(--accent);font-size:0.9rem;margin-bottom:14px;letter-spacing:2px;}
  .social-card p{font-size:0.92rem;color:var(--text-dim);margin-bottom:18px;}
  .social-author{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;}
  .social-avatar{
    width:38px;height:38px;border-radius:50%;
    background:var(--surface3);
    display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
    font-weight:700;font-size:0.85rem;color:var(--accent);
  }
  .social-name{font-weight:600;font-size:0.9rem;}
  .social-role{font-size:0.78rem;color:var(--text-dimmer);}

  /* ---------- FAQ ---------- */
  .faq-list{max-width:760px;margin:0 auto;}
  .faq-item{
    border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .faq-q{
    display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;
    padding:22px 4px;cursor:pointer;
    font-weight:600;font-size:1rem;
  }
  .faq-q svg{transition:transform .25s ease;color:var(--accent);flex-shrink:0;}
  .faq-item.open .faq-q svg{transform:rotate(45deg);}
  .faq-a{
    max-height:0;overflow:hidden;
    transition:max-height .3s ease;
  }
  .faq-a p{padding:0 4px 22px;color:var(--text-dim);font-size:0.92rem;max-width:640px;}
  .faq-item.open .faq-a{max-height:240px;}

  /* ---------- Final CTA ---------- */
  .final-cta{
    position:relative;
    text-align:center;
    background:linear-gradient(160deg, var(--surface2), var(--bg));
    border-top:1px solid var(--border);
    overflow:hidden;
  }
  .final-cta::before{
    content:'';position:absolute;
    bottom:-300px;left:50%;transform:translateX(-50%);
    width:800px;height:600px;
    background:radial-gradient(circle, rgba(200,245,66,0.12), transparent 70%);
    pointer-events:none;
  }
  .final-cta h2{font-size:clamp(1.9rem,4.5vw,2.8rem);margin-bottom:16px;position:relative;}
  .final-cta p{color:var(--text-dim);max-width:520px;margin:0 auto 32px;position:relative;}
  .final-cta .hero-actions{justify-content:center;position:relative;}

  /* ---------- Footer ---------- */
  footer{
    border-top:1px solid var(--border);
    padding:36px 0;
    text-align:center;
    color:var(--text-dimmer);font-size:0.84rem;
  }
  footer .logo{font-size:1.1rem;margin-bottom:10px;display:block;}

  /* ---------- WhatsApp floating button ---------- */
  .wa-float{
    position:fixed;bottom:22px;right:22px;z-index:200;
    width:58px;height:58px;border-radius:50%;
    background:var(--accent);color:var(--bg);
    display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
    box-shadow:0 12px 30px -8px rgba(200,245,66,0.5);
    transition:transform .2s ease;
  }
  .wa-float:hover{transform:scale(1.08);}

  /* ---------- Responsive ---------- */
  @media(max-width:920px){
    .hero-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;text-align:center;}
    .hero p.lead{margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;}
    .hero-actions{justify-content:center;}
    .hero-proof{justify-content:center;}
    .hero-visual{margin-top:20px;}
    .problem-grid, .social-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;}
    .modalities-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;}
    .how-grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);gap:36px 0;}
    .pricing-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;max-width:420px;margin:0 auto;}
    .freq-grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);}
    .objectives-grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);}
  }
  @media(max-width:520px){
    .how-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;}
    .freq-grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);}
    .objectives-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;}
    section{padding:64px 0;}
    .float-badge{display:none;}
    .phone{width:100%;max-width:280px;}
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
  <nav>
    <div class="logo">i9<span>Treino</span></div>
    <a href="#planos" class="nav-cta">Quero treinar</a>
  </nav>
</header>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="wrap hero-grid">
    <div>
      <div class="eyebrow">Treino online com acompanhamento real</div>
      <h1>Seu treino, na sua mão, <span class="accent">do seu jeito.</span></h1>
      <p class="lead">Musculação, CrossFit, HYROX ou corrida — protocolos completos, organizados por semana, com suas cargas salvas automaticamente toda vez que você treina.</p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a href="#planos" class="btn btn-primary">Quero meu protocolo</a>
        <a href="#como-funciona" class="btn btn-ghost">Como funciona</a>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-proof">
        <div>
          <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"/></svg>
          Protocolo pronto na hora
        </div>
        <div>
          <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"/></svg>
          Acompanhamento de evolução
        </div>
        <div>
          <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"/></svg>
          Funciona no celular, sem instalar nada
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-visual">
      <div class="phone">
        <div class="phone-screen">
          <div class="phone-app-name">i9<span class="accent">Treino</span></div>
          <div class="phone-app-sub">Semana 3 · Treino B — Peito e Tríceps</div>

          <div class="phone-card">
            <span class="phone-tag">Em andamento</span>
            <div class="phone-card-title" style="margin-top:10px;">Supino reto com halter</div>
            <div class="phone-card-meta">4 séries · 8 a 15 repetições</div>
            <div class="phone-row">
              <span class="phone-card-meta">Carga (kg)</span>
              <input class="load-input" value="22" readonly>
            </div>
